{"tid":1418243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係和理非","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T19:50:23.000Z","uid":51723,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"432b5494b9350af6ce940506ccab5a7e5851685e","tid":1418243,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:10:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我再講多一次，永遠唔會同前線割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n特別係抗爭都未完，就不斷出反思嘅post 係好discouraging。你諗下前線嘅手足落完場一打開部手機係咩感受？<br />\n<br />\n我相信不論前線、和理非都有改善嘅空間，但講睇法時，可否嘗試理解唔同身位嘅處境同感受，放下大家軍司嘅姿態<br />\n<br />\n唔知係有三毛定真心，我覺得今日連登個氣氛好差，好打擊士氣<br />\n<br />\n我想同其他和理非講，不如我哋襯呢段時間諗下點同其他市民解釋，爭取更多人支持。例如用武力去制服黑社會，係保護緊大家安全<br />\n<br />\n最後，抗爭係無得停架，警犬一直拉得就拉，檢控一樣會繼續架<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋輸唔起呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"b095b8f690c26fe98e05213b106758811028a128","tid":1418243,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割蓆<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418188</a>"},{"pid":"becd8e0b8a5e0efef4e03f16e7c69166954ed752","tid":1418243,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:11:21.000Z","msg":"認同，推!"},{"pid":"6a032dc6c449d7cca76612d3d67052a2a1a2c591","tid":1418243,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcbc2b1cb954c33c4271d2115e1959522eff572","tid":1418243,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:21.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n好多都係帶風向po"},{"pid":"ffad01e597c9231c1e187d3946316239c393b979","tid":1418243,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"創意救港，和理非手足入<br />\n有冇人想成立禮貌小隊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418111</a>"},{"pid":"c31ca4891dac663ea4d588c850546b1198fcc899","tid":1418243,"uid":33786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔撚割蓆啊屌你<br />\n<br />\n出面個極快升正皮POST真係好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n大家係想做D野就去站務台開POST/推POST叫連仔搞搞P仔正負皮既問題"},{"pid":"f80ef77030bd8776039ef0c0bc43d2ccd3c914c0","tid":1418243,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31ca4891dac663ea4d588c850546b1198fcc899","tid":1418243,"uid":33786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔撚割蓆啊屌你<br />\n<br />\n出面個極快升正皮POST真係好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n大家係想做D野就去站務台開POST/推POST叫連仔搞搞P仔正負皮既問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff60dfa018ae5a4d0344a023a345394771de14ea","tid":1418243,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80ef77030bd8776039ef0c0bc43d2ccd3c914c0","tid":1418243,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31ca4891dac663ea4d588c850546b1198fcc899","tid":1418243,"uid":33786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔撚割蓆啊屌你<br />\n<br />\n出面個極快升正皮POST真係好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n大家係想做D野就去站務台開POST/推POST叫連仔搞搞P仔正負皮既問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92f65b77e691fcc8b8f5abf8777d4af80079c79","tid":1418243,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:14:08.000Z","msg":"有巴打經歷咗呢幾日嘅事唔係太頂得順，希望大家可以幫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投降啦！我投降啦！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417937</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f849c8df1840b6aaed4365e4630f4bff4e379d2","tid":1418243,"uid":276838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"我相信前線 我更相信而家多左人和 唔好搞鳩前線 今日打幾場硬戰 甚至好多街坊見到勇武係會開心，前線係除惡 唔係周圍聊交打 請愛惜前線"},{"pid":"de5fefaa24ac6194594ea92b9976689bbe428b31","tid":1418243,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:14:36.000Z","msg":"我知道香港好多人都係和理非，既然硬碰硬比較難做到，咁破壞香港經濟亦未嘗唔係一個好方法，破壞經濟對一個政權嚟講亦係一個毀滅性打擊，大家之前講嘅<span style=\"color: gold;\">提擠中資銀行、罷工罷市或者其他不合作運動</span>，其實目的都係破壞經濟，如果係罷工罷市，請盡量將消息廣傳出去令更多人參加，只要數量夠多，歷史上冇任何一個政權可以扺擋到呢個經濟重創<br />\n<br />\n合法性動搖極權經濟舉偶：<br />\n<br />\n1.）大家養成一個習慣，將賺返嚟嘅錢存入外資銀行戶口（匯豐、恆生、渣打、花旗銀行等），冇就開一個，並且提擠中資銀行原本有嘅錢轉移至外資銀行<br />\n2.）幫各區連儂牆整理工作，本地旅遊區&amp;網絡上向國際嘅文宣工作（民陣已經向世界各國要求對港實行旅遊警示）<br />\n3.）再進一步嘅可以呼籲揀一日準備全民罷工罷市<br />\n4.）長期嘅不合作運動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共作為一個極權，好多錢都會放咗喺維穏費度，既然佢都係用啲錢去對付返人民，我地亦冇必要幫佢維持經濟發展"},{"pid":"3f2d4cef7c1d322fa85b01be74a4b6e24d7bf4da","tid":1418243,"uid":99608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"我都係和理非，再講多次，我本人包括身邊所有和理非冇話過前線一句，大家有出黎遊行發夢既，都會有眼睇前線幾搏命，唔分化！！！！！"},{"pid":"a76784582cc2b3434e4e5ca0299602462907a46a","tid":1418243,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:16:08.000Z","msg":"再post: 文宣攻勢開始啦，打左啲野大家幫手spread啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzDqbU1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzDqbU1.png&h=e9e101a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9724e9da535dbdfbf9cada18ed3dd9993a24e543","tid":1418243,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f2d4cef7c1d322fa85b01be74a4b6e24d7bf4da","tid":1418243,"uid":99608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"我都係和理非，再講多次，我本人包括身邊所有和理非冇話過前線一句，大家有出黎遊行發夢既，都會有眼睇前線幾搏命，唔分化！！！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"無錯，我今日都喺現場<br />\n明明身邊都無和理非話前線<br />\n唔明點解上連登會有咁多對前線不認同"},{"pid":"34c0744987d149ccfe10833f91cef839e7c3597c","tid":1418243,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:20:37.000Z","msg":"不分化、不篤灰、不割蓆"},{"pid":"9e998f37ccf59d1107c6e6659285827cf9e883f1","tid":1418243,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:24:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7aaedcc0f14c058f921cf6ae4611841f3872b3e","tid":1418243,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:28:13.000Z","msg":"推到比前線睇到"},{"pid":"b602f313bade9fc5dbaadcffbfe11edbcbfbe41e","tid":1418243,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:28:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8134362245bd851cbad0f6b32f76a5e1ad482b48","tid":1418243,"uid":51723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:29:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73f4ba721fb895b88fcd86201f62dfe454284307","tid":1418243,"uid":141545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:50:23.000Z","msg":"前線你地真係好勇 加油！"}]}